 atlases, books or periodicals, and printed facsimiles. These maps may also show various subjects, such as land owners and recreation and tourism. To request a specific map or for more information, contact a reference librarian in the Geography & Map Division (202) 707-6277 or through the \"Ask a librarian\" link through the Geography & Map Division website https://ask.loc.gov/map-geography/. Title supplied by cataloger."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:17:43.053Z", "group": ["gmd/multimap", "catalog-split-03", "catalog", "multimaps", "main-catalog-split-03"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2022594830/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolfold:ct:-0:84:ct-084:ct-084-00001/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolfold:ct:-0:84:ct-084:ct-084-00001/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=453&w=348", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolfold:ct:-0:84:ct-084:ct-084-00001/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=906&w=696"], "index": 10, "language": ["english"], "location": ["connecticut", "united states", "waterbury"], "mime_type": ["image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2025-06-07t11:52:01.400000", "2022594830", "sheet", "2024-05-11t20:47:42"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map", "collection"], "other_title": ["Alternate supplied title: Connecticut title collection--drawer 84", "Alternate supplied title: Connecticut title collection--cities and towns Waterbury 1906-1939"], "partof": ["geography and map division", "catalog", "single sheet maps, title collection"], "score": 29.786396, "shelf_id": "G3784.W3 coll .M3 drawer 84", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["waterbury (conn.)", "landowners", "tourist maps", "united states", "waterbury", "connecticut", "maps"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:32:48.014Z", "title": "[Maps of Connecticut--cities and towns Waterbury 1906-1939]", "type": ["cartograp